School of IT recently opened their doors in Somerset West (155 main road, Somerset West). The training provider offers both online and face-to-face tuition in the South Africa and abroad. They offer a wide variety of courses, including programming courses, Data Science, Web Design, SQL, PC Engineering, AutoCad, Social media, Graphic Design, and MS Office. Programming courses include C#, Java, Python, Android and C++. They also offer great Coding Bootcamps in Johannesburg, Cape Town and abroad. School of IT focuses on the practical side of programming and IT. Enrol today at https://www.schoolofit.co.za/. This article was published in partnership with School of IT.